data.description: Discover coastal elegance at 2609 Seagirt Ave, Far Rockaway. This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and beachside charm. Immerse yourself in natural light throughout the open living spaces, enjoy a stylish kitchen, and relax in the spacious bedrooms. With a private backyard oasis, proximity to the beach, and convenient access to local amenities, this residence is an invitation to a relaxed, coastal lifestyle. Welcome home to Seagirt Avenue!
